PP3V3_S5 = 0.454V
PP3V3_SUS = 0,024V
PPBUS_G3H = 8.60V
PP5V_S5 = 0.125V - falling !
PP5V_S4RS3 = 0.00V

I hope thats all you need :)

Greetings !
